Interface Person

All Known Implementing Classes:
PersonRow
public interface Person

Represents a single row of the Person table.

Some relevant facts about this interface:

  • It represents the data that can be stored and retrieved from the Person table in the database.
  • It has 15 columns, all of which have getter and setter methods.
